{
  "name": "NegativeBarFormat",
  "summary": "<p><strong>NegativeBarFormat</strong> 对象的属性可用来指定负值数据条的填充色和边框。使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Databar/Databar .htm#Databar.Databar\">Databar</a></strong> 对象的表示数据条条件格式规则的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Databar/Databar .htm#Databar.NegativeBarFormat\">NegativeBarFormat</a></strong> 可访问与该规则关联的 <strong>NegativeBarFormat</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的主题颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent2\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent2\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第二个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条与正数据条相同的填充颜色，则将该负数据条设置为与正数据条相同的边框颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> == xlDataBarSameAsPositive) {\n        databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColorType</span> = xlDataBarSameAsPositive\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示由数据条条件格式规则定义的负值的数据条颜色设置。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "BorderColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong> 对象，可使用该对象指定负数据条的边框色。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的填充颜色和边框颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第二个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的边框颜色和亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong>FormatColor</strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "BorderColorType",
      "summary": "<p>如果将 <strong>BorderColorType</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlDataBarColor</strong>, 那么使用 <strong>NegativeBarFormat</strong> 的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/NegativeBarFormat/NegativeBarFormat .htm#NegativeBarFormat.BorderColor\">BorderColor</a></strong> 可返回 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong> 对象，可使用该对象来指定边框色。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>指定是否使用与正数据条相同的边框色。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第二个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的边框色是否使用在“负值和轴设置”对话框中指定的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColorType</span> == xlDataBarColor)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的填充颜色，并将边框颜色设置与正值数据条相同。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColorType</span> = xlDataBarSameAsPositive\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlDataBarNegativeColorType 枚举.html\">XlDataBarNegativeColorType</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong> 对象，可使用该对象来指定负数据条的填充色。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的填充颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第二个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的填充颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorType",
      "summary": "<p>如果将 <strong>ColorType</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlDataBarColor</strong>, 那么使用 <strong>NegativeBarFormat</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/NegativeBarFormat/NegativeBarFormat .htm#NegativeBarFormat.Color\">Color</a></strong> 可返回 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong> 对象，可使用该对象来指定填充色。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>指定是否使用与正数据条相同的填充色。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第二个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条的填充色是否使用在“负值和轴设置”对话框中指定的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> == xlDataBarColor)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个条件格式（数据条）的负数据条设置为与正数据条相同的填充颜色和边框颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> databar = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> = xlDataBarSameAsPositive\n    databar.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NegativeBarFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BorderColorType</span> = xlDataBarSameAsPositive\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlDataBarNegativeColorType 枚举.html\">XlDataBarNegativeColorType</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    }
